### =========================================================
### User Auth API - Authorization Evaluate
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@accessToken = 4bd0892d-d7b5-4748-a56d-0f7e2f4aa2f0
@tenantId = REPLACE_TENANT_ID
@resourceRef = passport_123

### 1) Evaluate - TOKEN_SNAPSHOT
POST {{baseUrl}}/authz/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "action": "RETAIL_RELEASE",
  "resourceRef": "{{resourceRef}}",
  "decisionMode": "TOKEN_SNAPSHOT"
}

### 2) Evaluate - LIVE_RECHECK (민감 액션 권장)
POST {{baseUrl}}/authz/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "action": "TENANT_ROLE_ASSIGN",
  "resourceRef": "membership:REPLACE_MEMBERSHIP_ID",
  "decisionMode": "LIVE_RECHECK"
}

### 3) Evaluate - tenant mismatch 예시 (deny 기대)
POST {{baseUrl}}/authz/evaluate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "tenantId": "wrong-tenant-id",
  "action": "RETAIL_RELEASE",
  "resourceRef": "{{resourceRef}}",
  "decisionMode": "TOKEN_SNAPSHOT"
}
